          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1696241163686-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the aubergine is tender, carefully scoop out the <strong>flesh</strong>, taking care not to break the skin, and roughly chop the flesh</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped aubergine flesh</strong> to the stuffing<strong> </strong>and mix it all together</p><p>Divide the<strong> aubergine stuffing</strong> between the <strong>aubergine skin[s]</strong> and top with the <strong>remaining goats' cheese</strong> and <strong>crushed walnuts</strong></p><p>Return the tray[s] to the oven and cook for 4-5 min or until the cheese has melted – this is your<strong> Italian-style stuffed aubergine</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1696241166933-x200.jpg",
