          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1696241166933-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1696241166933-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add the <strong>remaining vegetable stock mix </strong>to your <strong>cooked rice</strong> with <strong>half </strong>the <strong>chopped parsley </strong>(save some for garnish!)</p><p>Give everything a good mix up and cook over a low heat for 1-2 min or until warmed through – this is your <strong>herby brown rice</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>baby leaf salad</strong>, then pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Toss the <strong>baby leaf salad </strong>with your <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong> and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> in a large bowl – this is your <strong>dressed salad</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
