          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1696241170531-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1696241170531-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> Italian-style stuffed aubergine </strong>with the <strong>herby brown rice </strong>and <strong>dressed salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Garnish the aubergine with the <strong>remaining chopped parsley</strong> and season with a pinch of <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
